{"tid":357487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關島發應對導彈小冊子教逃生","createTime":"2017-08-13T01:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T02:42:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53da54e2371dea38cab74cfd8b6aa0a149760467","tid":357487,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:58:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20120047&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20120047%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170813&d=m616hwsrpu5MMXD4e9O1jxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=02151dbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20120047%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170813&h=9c571211\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20120047&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170813</a><br />\n<br />\n關島發應對導彈小冊子教逃生<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n關島有居民到超市買樽裝水以備不時之需。<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n北韓日前威脅發射四枚導彈包圍關島，關島國土安全部門未敢輕視，前日發佈應對導彈攻擊措施的小冊子，包括準備逃生用的背包、如何清除身上的放射性物質和不要直視火球等。<br />\n國土安全部發佈一份兩頁、名為《防範緊急情況──為迫在眉睫的導彈威脅作準備》的小冊子，指出若離爆炸中心有一段距離、衝擊波或需30秒以上方會抵達，民眾應依循預早想好在住所、辦公室等附近的逃生路線，當局發出警戒時躲到由混凝土或磚頭所建的建築物。<br />\n<br />\n若衣物、皮膚或毛髮沾上放射性物質，除下衣物足以清除九成放射性物質，用大量肥皂及水沖身，清洗鼻孔、耳孔和眼瞼，但避免抓或擦皮膚，且不能用護髮素，否則放射性物質會黏住毛髮。小冊子亦列明「不要直視閃光或火球──可致盲」。<br />\n不過，關島官員並未有提高當地的警戒水平，而今次的小冊子亦是早於四年前便因應類似威脅已準備好，當地社會並未陷入恐慌。美國總統特朗普與關島總督卡爾沃通電，前者「1000%」保證關島安全，後者則表示對特朗普政府有信心。<br />\n美聯社/美國《華盛頓郵報》<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n孩子在關島一個紀念公園展出的一枚二戰炮彈上玩耍。路透社<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n北韓籌謀海上試射導彈<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;4小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n南韓人買金避險　即食食品大賣<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;4小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n美朝連日互兇　局勢隨時惡化習勸特朗普勿再挑釁北韓<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;4小時前"},{"pid":"9a2c2c0d15692df2c12b654df412fc0a20c170c8","tid":357487,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170813/large/13we6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170813%2Flarge%2F13we6p.jpg&h=8ee40e18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關島有居民到超市買樽裝水以備不時之需。<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"23f4285893b6a4557c3e3d342f086e8986c7f1d6","tid":357487,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:02:15.000Z","msg":"午餐肉"},{"pid":"2dd766b6fe440f39a4c0120296b23ab49c21586e","tid":357487,"uid":43361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人去關島？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483d4bef33ce6d2b4aef7158aa1d54ccea736e1b","tid":357487,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170813/large/13we6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170813%2Flarge%2F13we6p.jpg&h=8ee40e18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關島有居民到超市買樽裝水以備不時之需。<br />\n美聯社</blockquote><br />\n第一眼睇想講「洗唔洗掃咁多啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n&hellip;我地真係太過太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593d85d43ef408e86adf5f0076270bd7c383ba7b","tid":357487,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img s